public class NullSvgPointException
extends java.lang.RuntimeException

This unchecked exception signals that the client application attempted to copy a Point object into a null reference.

NullSvgPointException

public NullSvgPointException(Point p)
Outputs basic message and the Point where the exception was thrown to be output. Do not pass the copy target; that would just be dumb.

Parameters:
p - You could pass any point you wish but the copier Point (the Point that is doing the copying) is the intension.

Outputs basic message and the Point where the exception was thrown to be output. Do not pass the copy target; that would just be dumb.

str - Alternate message you wish to include along with the Point's toString() data.
